/-- The `simp_lists_simps` simp attribute. -/
initialize simpListsSimpExt : SimpExtension ←
  registerSimpAttr `simp_lists_simps "\
    The `simp_lists_simps` attribute registers simp lemmas to be used by `simp_lists`."

